      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if those mandates are actually important for everyone? like if a religious group opts out of a public health mandate or some kind of civil rights law, isn't that basically saying their beliefs are more important than the safety or equality of the rest of society? doesn't that kind of undermine the whole point of having laws that apply to everyone equally?",
